HEADWORD: Offender
<hw>Of*fend"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who offends;
one who violates any law, divine or human; a wrongdoer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I and my son Solomon shall be counted <qex>offenders</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>1 Kings i. 21.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Offendress</ent>⟦br⟧
